WEBVTT

00:34.520 --> 00:35.470
Xiao Wuyi!

00:38.560 --> 00:40.000
Xiao Wuyi!

00:49.110 --> 00:50.030
It's Young Master Yao!

00:50.030 --> 00:51.030
Young Master Yao?

00:52.920 --> 00:54.180
He's still breathing.

00:54.200 --> 00:55.460
Where is His Highness?

00:59.320 --> 01:00.880
You're going to the battlefield,

01:00.880 --> 01:02.540
so you deserve the best horse.

01:02.560 --> 01:03.760
It can bring you home.

01:10.510 --> 01:11.680
Xiao Wuyi!

01:11.710 --> 01:12.640
Your Highness!

01:12.640 --> 01:13.789
Your Highness!

01:25.590 --> 01:26.789
Xiao Wuyi!

01:39.229 --> 01:40.039
Xiao Wuyi!

01:48.710 --> 01:50.640
I'll accept your Black Iron Sword.

01:57.350 --> 01:57.920
Yaoyao,

01:58.710 --> 01:59.560
you said you've been learning

01:59.560 --> 02:01.290
to say goodbye your whole life.

02:01.510 --> 02:02.480
So have I.

02:03.640 --> 02:04.770
My parents are gone.

02:05.230 --> 02:06.360
My homeland is lost.

02:06.950 --> 02:07.840
A name and a mission were

02:07.840 --> 02:08.750
forced upon me.

02:09.710 --> 02:10.840
Living in the world,

02:10.910 --> 02:12.400
I got to understand its ways,

02:12.400 --> 02:13.660
yet failing the grace.

02:14.800 --> 02:17.000
What I gained in my life is what I sought.

02:17.310 --> 02:19.240
Yet it is somehow not what I sought.

02:19.750 --> 02:21.520
There is neither anyone to blame

02:21.520 --> 02:23.380
nor anywhere to direct my hatred.

02:25.030 --> 02:26.690
The way of heaven is ruthless.

02:27.079 --> 02:29.079
Blood drenched the Central Plains.

02:29.120 --> 02:31.380
Women and children were reduced to dust.

02:31.750 --> 02:33.550
Though I'm merely a human being,

02:33.710 --> 02:35.370
I'm willing to be the backbone

02:35.960 --> 02:37.630
to rebuild the nation anew.

02:41.000 --> 02:41.590
Yaoyao,

02:42.310 --> 02:43.710
since you've made your promise,

02:43.710 --> 02:46.440
no matter who tries
to take you away in the future,

02:47.800 --> 02:49.560
I will never let you go again.

02:52.170 --> 02:53.640
But 3 months is too short.

02:57.470 --> 02:58.560
How about 3 years?

02:59.840 --> 03:01.840
Can't you just say you'll try harder

03:01.870 --> 03:02.870
to stay alive?

03:06.800 --> 03:07.520
Okay.

03:12.750 --> 03:14.750
Xiao Wuyi!

03:23.520 --> 03:25.560
Xiao Wuyi!

05:39.900 --> 05:44.050
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

05:44.110 --> 05:47.010
[Episode 28]

05:48.270 --> 05:50.670
[Three years later, First Year of Hong]

05:50.870 --> 05:51.730
Is that the end?

05:51.950 --> 05:52.800
What about Xiao Wuyi?

05:52.800 --> 05:53.860
Is he dead or alive?

05:54.190 --> 05:55.120
Did the Xiao family really harm

05:55.120 --> 05:56.630
the An and Lu families back then?

05:56.630 --> 05:58.630
Did we win the battle at Dingfeng Slope?

05:58.630 --> 06:00.270
We won, of course!

06:01.000 --> 06:01.630
If not,

06:01.720 --> 06:03.630
why would His Majesty re-establish
Chang County in the northwest?

06:03.630 --> 06:04.240
That's right.

06:04.240 --> 06:06.510
The Xiao family has even
drafted a confession letter.

06:06.510 --> 06:08.000
It couldn't be fake, could it?

06:08.000 --> 06:10.330
Exactly! In the battle at Dingfeng Slope,

06:10.390 --> 06:12.720
our Ye's 40,000 Beifu soldiers

06:12.920 --> 06:15.450
confronted
Northern Qin's 100,000 soldiers

06:15.950 --> 06:19.070
and completely routed Northern Qin.

06:19.560 --> 06:22.950
In this battle, they not only wiped out
the main force of the Northern Qin army

06:22.950 --> 06:25.510
but also allowed 100,000 Ye citizens

06:25.510 --> 06:27.390
to return home safely.

06:27.830 --> 06:29.230
With the Eagle King dead,

06:29.510 --> 06:33.070
the little emperor of Northern Qin was
wary of his meritorious officials,

06:33.070 --> 06:35.360
causing chaos at the imperial court.

06:36.000 --> 06:39.120
And our Ye's Beifu soldiers,
after Prince Qi's...

06:39.140 --> 06:39.700
No,

06:39.920 --> 06:43.430
after His Majesty's Beifu Reform,

06:43.750 --> 06:45.310
they've made an army
of elite soldiers and generals,

06:45.310 --> 06:46.920
with the soldiers
and the people of one mind.

06:46.920 --> 06:50.630
This is all thanks to His Majesty.

06:50.750 --> 06:52.210
All thanks to His Majesty?

06:53.310 --> 06:54.680
I remember the Beifu Reform

06:54.680 --> 06:56.740
was first proposed by Xiao Wuyi, right?

06:56.740 --> 06:58.120
In the battle at Dingfeng Slope,

06:58.120 --> 06:59.600
were it not for him who risked his life,

06:59.600 --> 07:01.310
how could we've held off
the Eagle King's main force?

07:01.310 --> 07:02.720
Were it not for His Majesty's support,

07:02.720 --> 07:03.720
could Xiao Wuyi have

07:03.720 --> 07:05.120
carried out this reform?

07:05.120 --> 07:05.950
-He's right.
-Indeed.

07:05.950 --> 07:06.920
If His Majesty hadn't led the troops

07:06.920 --> 07:07.790
and united the soldiers,

07:07.790 --> 07:08.830
Xiao Wuyi would've

07:08.830 --> 07:09.830
died for nothing.

07:11.680 --> 07:12.750
Stop talking nonsense!

07:12.750 --> 07:14.070
That's not right.

07:14.750 --> 07:17.510
Back then,
were it not for Young Lord Xiao's support,

07:17.510 --> 07:18.270
His Majesty

07:18.390 --> 07:20.360
wouldn't have secured
his position as Regent.

07:20.360 --> 07:21.600
It's all in the past.

07:22.070 --> 07:23.270
Nowadays, His Majesty

07:23.270 --> 07:25.070
works day and night diligently,

07:25.360 --> 07:26.950
promotes talents from poor backgrounds,

07:26.950 --> 07:28.430
and abolishes harsh laws.

07:28.680 --> 07:30.880
His Majesty has the aura of a wise ruler.

07:31.630 --> 07:32.310
Anyway,

07:32.600 --> 07:34.159
is Xiao Wuyi dead or not?

07:34.159 --> 07:35.310
To explain it,

07:35.800 --> 07:37.000
we have to talk about

07:37.000 --> 07:39.270
the firearms
used on the battlefield that day,

07:39.270 --> 07:40.600
the caltrop fireballs!

07:41.110 --> 07:43.840
Looks like it's time for me
to return to Jiankang.

07:55.159 --> 07:55.950
Lady Yu,

07:56.510 --> 07:57.510
your son

07:58.000 --> 08:00.120
didn't come to the clinic with you today?

08:00.120 --> 08:00.920
He set up

08:00.920 --> 08:02.240
a trap at school today,

08:02.430 --> 08:04.120
splashing slops all over his teacher.

08:04.120 --> 08:06.320
The teacher made him stay to copy texts.

08:07.040 --> 08:09.310
Teenage boys always like making trouble.

08:09.310 --> 08:10.070
Yeah,

08:10.240 --> 08:11.360
I'm wondering who he takes after,

08:11.360 --> 08:13.070
tinkering with mechanisms every day.

08:13.070 --> 08:14.630
His father, his teacher, and I

08:14.630 --> 08:15.630
are not like that.

08:16.800 --> 08:17.600
Really?

08:26.730 --> 08:28.630
[Zhengtong Bookstore]

08:44.150 --> 08:44.870
Lady He.

08:46.120 --> 08:47.250
Here in the academy,

08:47.360 --> 08:48.420
I'm only a teacher.

08:49.550 --> 08:50.610
Greetings, Ms. He.

08:51.600 --> 08:53.720
Today we are studying the Announcement
of Duke Shao from the Book of Documents.

08:53.720 --> 08:54.720
Have you looked through it?

08:54.720 --> 08:56.870
Yes, we have.

09:00.200 --> 09:02.240
I don't have a copy of the Announcement

09:02.240 --> 09:03.770
of Duke Shao due to poverty.

09:07.240 --> 09:09.390
This bookstore now belongs to me.

09:10.150 --> 09:12.150
It stores the He family's book collection.

09:12.150 --> 09:13.080
Starting today,

09:13.200 --> 09:15.320
you can borrow and copy books as you like.

09:15.320 --> 09:17.000
I will only charge for ink and paper.

09:17.000 --> 09:18.270
Thank you, Ms. He.

09:18.550 --> 09:19.670
Thank you, Ms. He.

09:20.080 --> 09:22.390
"I plant beans
beneath the southern hills."

09:22.390 --> 09:24.440
"The weeds flourish,
yet the bean sprouts are sparse."

09:24.440 --> 09:27.500
"The weeds flourish,
yet the bean sprouts are sparse."

09:35.000 --> 09:36.390
Couldn't I just have it expedited back

09:36.390 --> 09:37.190
on horseback?

09:37.390 --> 09:39.650
Why did I have to bring it back
to Jiankang in person?

09:39.650 --> 09:43.080
[Li Mao, Emperor of Ye]

09:40.870 --> 09:43.030
The mineral map is a national secret.

09:43.630 --> 09:45.630
How could it be entrusted to others?

09:49.000 --> 09:51.530
These two places are
where the iron mines are.

09:53.390 --> 09:54.360
More mining?

09:54.870 --> 09:56.080
Are we going to war again?

09:56.080 --> 09:58.410
The Northern Qin's young emperor is dead.

09:59.600 --> 10:01.600
Rumor has it he was poisoned to death.

10:01.600 --> 10:02.670
The Eagle King's death

10:02.670 --> 10:04.960
dealt a devastating blow
to the Northern Qin's foundation.

10:04.960 --> 10:06.390
Now their princes are having infighting

10:06.390 --> 10:07.550
and ruling on their own.

10:07.550 --> 10:09.200
They're also facing the invasion
of Rong and Qiang.

10:09.200 --> 10:09.840
It's the perfect time

10:09.840 --> 10:12.630
for us to reclaim the Capital
in one fell swoop.

10:14.550 --> 10:17.750
Do you know that Northern Qin
has put a bounty on your head,

10:17.870 --> 10:19.720
and it's gone up to 1,000 taels of gold
in the black market now?

10:19.720 --> 10:21.650
Because of the caltrop fireballs?

10:22.510 --> 10:23.970
Then let them come and try.

10:24.790 --> 10:26.870
I know your lightness skill is
exceptional now,

10:26.870 --> 10:28.910
and you don't need anyone
to protect you at all.

10:28.910 --> 10:29.790
You even sent Qing Long

10:29.790 --> 10:31.120
and Yan Yue back to Beifu

10:31.320 --> 10:32.850
to be regional commanders.

10:34.080 --> 10:34.880
It's just that

10:36.200 --> 10:38.200
you used to love a lively atmosphere.

10:38.200 --> 10:40.200
Now traveling the world on your own,

10:40.390 --> 10:41.650
don't you feel lonely?

10:43.910 --> 10:45.840
Someone is with me on the same path,

10:45.960 --> 10:47.490
so I have never felt lonely.

11:04.120 --> 11:05.270
I felt something was wrong with you
when we tested

11:05.270 --> 11:06.790
the caltrop fireballs yesterday.

11:06.790 --> 11:07.650
What happened?

11:07.670 --> 11:09.550
There are too many impurities
in the stone fat.

11:09.550 --> 11:11.080
Inhaling it into the lungs when it burns

11:11.080 --> 11:11.810
causes this.

11:12.440 --> 11:13.240
What's more,

11:14.200 --> 11:16.330
the land where the stone fat has burned

11:16.790 --> 11:18.590
will be left completely barren.

11:18.670 --> 11:20.030
I have destroyed the designs

11:20.030 --> 11:21.490
for the caltrop fireball.

11:21.910 --> 11:23.160
The burned land at Dingfeng Slope

11:23.160 --> 11:24.240
back then

11:24.270 --> 11:25.730
could no longer be farmed.

11:26.240 --> 11:27.700
One deterrence is enough.

11:28.030 --> 11:29.480
If you insist on using caltrop fireballs

11:29.480 --> 11:30.750
to fight your way back to the Capital,

11:30.750 --> 11:32.150
you will lose people's support.

11:32.150 --> 11:34.370
Even if you trap me here
in Jiankang Palace,

11:34.370 --> 11:35.630
I still won't help you.

11:35.840 --> 11:37.440
Nobody asked you about this.

11:38.030 --> 11:39.150
Aren't you curious

11:39.390 --> 11:40.630
about the Beifu Commander

11:40.630 --> 11:42.290
for the expedition this time?

11:44.000 --> 11:45.400
It's none of my business.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.550
I appointed Old General Ruan,

11:48.550 --> 11:49.960
from the Beifu Yafu Camp.

11:50.790 --> 11:52.390
Only then did I find out that,

11:52.440 --> 11:53.500
during the Reform,

11:53.600 --> 11:56.080
Xiao Wuyi had been
training the camps to coordinate

11:56.080 --> 11:57.910
to restore the supervisory system.

11:57.910 --> 11:59.390
I suppose that was also when

11:59.390 --> 12:00.440
he started preparing for what

12:00.440 --> 12:02.100
would happen after his death.

12:02.270 --> 12:03.960
He was afraid
that one day when he was gone,

12:03.960 --> 12:05.290
the sharp blade of Beifu

12:05.440 --> 12:07.240
would hurt Ye instead.

12:08.360 --> 12:09.390
So he was trying

12:09.870 --> 12:10.790
to create a Beifu Army

12:10.790 --> 12:12.120
that would still fight

12:12.600 --> 12:13.480
for the people of Ye

12:13.480 --> 12:15.200
even without Xiao Wuyi.

12:19.150 --> 12:21.270
The one I sent
to supervise Beifu this time

12:21.270 --> 12:23.800
is my most trusted
Imperial Guard Commander.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.930
He used to be a member of Beifu, too.

12:26.030 --> 12:27.790
He was injured on the battlefield,

12:27.790 --> 12:28.650
and I saved him.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.690
Then we became sworn brothers.

12:31.150 --> 12:31.790
I trust him

12:32.600 --> 12:34.460
even more than I trusted Wuyi back then.

12:34.460 --> 12:36.920
I was still willing
to deliver this map today

12:36.960 --> 12:39.090
because if Xiao Wuyi were still alive,

12:39.150 --> 12:41.480
he'd definitely want me to come in person.

12:42.510 --> 12:44.370
He always wanted to see Ye reclaim

12:44.470 --> 12:46.360
its lost territory, including the Capital,

12:46.360 --> 12:47.360
with his own eyes.

12:47.910 --> 12:50.040
As for what you plan to do with the Beifu

12:50.090 --> 12:52.030
and who you plan to use to replace him,

12:52.030 --> 12:53.090
I don't care at all.

12:54.170 --> 12:54.970
Your Majesty,

12:55.680 --> 12:56.940
you've forgotten him.

12:57.000 --> 12:58.360
The world has forgotten him.

12:58.360 --> 12:59.160
But I haven't,

13:01.320 --> 13:02.480
and I never will.

13:08.230 --> 13:09.630
Jiankang is way too cold.

13:11.240 --> 13:13.100
I will never come back here again.

13:20.910 --> 13:22.570
She's still so hot-tempered.

13:36.390 --> 13:38.450
Where on earth is the Guangyang Gate?

13:46.790 --> 13:48.200
Which way should I go?

13:48.750 --> 13:49.480
Who's there?

13:53.320 --> 13:54.080
Who are you?

13:55.480 --> 13:56.870
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

13:56.870 --> 13:58.470
His Majesty invited me over.

13:58.480 --> 13:59.810
Why don't you go ask him?

14:05.270 --> 14:06.200
I wouldn't dare.

14:06.390 --> 14:07.920
Greetings, Your Highness.

14:08.440 --> 14:10.300
How do I get to the Guangyang Gate?

14:32.080 --> 14:33.030
Acting mysterious.

14:33.030 --> 14:35.230
Dare you go fight on a real battlefield?

14:56.510 --> 14:57.970
Commander, what's wrong?

15:00.480 --> 15:01.440
I'm fine.

15:02.630 --> 15:03.630
It's an old wound.

15:20.360 --> 15:22.600
Have you forgotten
what the miraculous doctor said?

15:22.600 --> 15:25.460
Your body won't allow you
to practice martial arts.

15:29.600 --> 15:30.870
Greetings, Your Majesty.

15:30.870 --> 15:31.510
Rise now.

15:36.720 --> 15:37.600
Given your physical condition,

15:37.600 --> 15:38.750
if you want to live long,

15:38.750 --> 15:40.150
you must rest well. Yet you insisted

15:40.150 --> 15:41.520
on going to the Northern Border.

15:41.520 --> 15:42.520
I've agreed to it.

15:43.120 --> 15:45.630
But I only allow you
to be a military supervisor.

15:45.630 --> 15:47.480
If you insist on going to the battlefield,

15:47.480 --> 15:49.000
I will issue an imperial edict

15:49.000 --> 15:50.600
to get you back immediately.

15:51.240 --> 15:52.630
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:55.240 --> 15:58.900
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an
came to the palace today.

15:59.510 --> 16:02.240
I heard you ran into each other
on the palace path.

16:04.550 --> 16:07.390
If I want to bring her into my harem,

16:08.840 --> 16:09.840
what do you think?

16:10.720 --> 16:11.550
I think...

16:20.670 --> 16:21.510
Never mind.

16:21.870 --> 16:23.080
She has deep affection

16:23.080 --> 16:24.150
for her husband.

16:24.670 --> 16:25.790
I am the Emperor.

16:26.550 --> 16:28.750
I can find any kind of beauty
in the future.

16:28.750 --> 16:30.480
Why limit myself to one person?

16:31.910 --> 16:33.910
Your main purpose
in going to the Northern Border this time

16:33.910 --> 16:35.310
is to mine the mountains.

16:36.080 --> 16:37.480
If you have any problems,

16:37.630 --> 16:38.960
ask the Heir's Consort.

16:44.120 --> 16:46.080
Your Majesty, I remember you once said

16:46.080 --> 16:48.540
that she owns the map
and caltrop fireballs.

16:49.000 --> 16:51.360
Are you truly going to let her
leave Jiankang?

16:51.360 --> 16:52.870
Do you have any better ideas?

16:52.870 --> 16:54.270
Why not detain her first,

16:54.390 --> 16:56.080
claim it's Northern Qin's doing,

16:56.080 --> 16:58.010
and use it as a valid reason for war?

16:58.840 --> 17:00.000
If I really detain her,

17:00.000 --> 17:02.330
she will blow up my whole Jiankang Palace.

17:02.390 --> 17:03.920
Even if she won't blow it up,

17:05.109 --> 17:07.480
I'm afraid
when a certain someone recalls everything,

17:07.480 --> 17:09.940
he will tear down
this Jiankang Palace, too.

17:13.440 --> 17:15.240
Life and death are

17:15.240 --> 17:16.839
the natural order of things.

17:16.920 --> 17:19.119
He's hurt this badly yet still not dead.

17:19.349 --> 17:20.790
What is it in this world

17:20.790 --> 17:22.650
that he clings to so desperately?

17:24.160 --> 17:26.480
Please save my brother, miraculous doctor.

17:26.480 --> 17:27.609
I heard that you have

17:27.750 --> 17:29.950
the power to bring the dead back to life.

17:30.270 --> 17:32.930
Now, only you can save my brother!

17:32.960 --> 17:34.720
That's not bringing the dead back to life.

17:34.720 --> 17:36.510
That's just because they weren't
truly dead.

17:36.510 --> 17:36.790
Wait!

17:36.790 --> 17:37.250
Doctor!

17:38.510 --> 17:40.440
Wuyi is still breathing right now.

17:40.950 --> 17:43.210
You once promised to save my life 3 times.

17:43.920 --> 17:45.590
Please fulfill your last promise.

17:45.590 --> 17:46.990
If you want me to save him,

17:47.030 --> 17:49.310
he must first be pushed
to the brink of death.

17:49.310 --> 17:51.170
It will require cutting him open.

17:51.400 --> 17:54.110
And even if he survives,
he will lose his memory.

17:56.510 --> 17:58.040
Whether he survives or dies

17:58.680 --> 17:59.720
is up to fate.

18:01.400 --> 18:03.330
I believe God will take pity on him.

18:04.000 --> 18:04.730
Don't worry.

18:05.270 --> 18:06.550
Xie Jiayu will be fine.

18:07.200 --> 18:08.880
And she will never betray Ye.

18:09.720 --> 18:11.270
You are going to the Northern Border.

18:11.270 --> 18:13.400
You still need a weapon that suits you.

18:13.750 --> 18:16.480
Miraculous Craft in Jiankang
can create anything.

18:16.480 --> 18:17.610
You can give it a try.

18:20.960 --> 18:22.020
Yes, Your Majesty.

18:26.680 --> 18:27.740
Miraculous Craft?

19:15.070 --> 19:16.790
Why did I draw this sword?

19:20.830 --> 19:22.480
-Great!
-Bravo!

19:27.680 --> 19:29.520
-Brilliant!
-Bravo!

19:28.690 --> 19:29.310
[Miraculous Craft]

19:31.270 --> 19:32.400
Is the manager here?

19:33.590 --> 19:34.440
The manager is not here.

19:34.440 --> 19:36.440
You can tell me if you have any needs.

19:36.960 --> 19:38.960
I heard that your workshop
can forge any kind of weapon

19:38.960 --> 19:40.760
according to the requirements.

19:41.160 --> 19:42.240
"Supervised by the government office.

19:42.240 --> 19:43.840
Honest with all customers."

19:44.000 --> 19:46.400
This is very exquisite.
Please take a look.

19:46.480 --> 19:47.030
This is not bad.

19:47.030 --> 19:47.440
Right?

19:48.750 --> 19:49.400
Okay.

19:50.000 --> 19:51.110
Come to pick it up in 3 months.

19:51.110 --> 19:52.170
It takes that long?

19:52.680 --> 19:53.720
I'm leaving soon.

19:54.200 --> 19:55.550
Can I talk to your manager in person?

19:55.550 --> 19:57.070
The manager doesn't meet people.

19:57.070 --> 19:58.400
This is a fixed rule.

19:58.640 --> 20:00.110
It's the same for everyone.

20:00.110 --> 20:01.110
If you can't wait,

20:01.440 --> 20:02.700
you'd better not wait.

20:04.850 --> 20:05.840
[Black Iron Sword]

20:06.670 --> 20:07.800
Who is your manager?

20:08.030 --> 20:09.110
The manager of our shop is

20:09.110 --> 20:10.350
the Grand Master

20:10.350 --> 20:12.070
of Beifu Directorate of Military Equipment

20:12.070 --> 20:14.930
as well as the Consort
of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

20:16.720 --> 20:19.050
The Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an?

20:21.400 --> 20:22.400
How much is the deposit?

20:22.400 --> 20:24.240
No deposit is needed. Our manager said

20:24.240 --> 20:24.790
she'll cover the cost

20:24.790 --> 20:27.000
of materials
if we fail to forge any items.

20:27.000 --> 20:28.400
What if I'm not in Jiankang

20:28.400 --> 20:29.550
when it's done?

20:29.830 --> 20:31.680
Don't worry. Our Miraculous Craft

20:31.680 --> 20:33.940
has branches in both Ye and Northern Qin.

20:34.030 --> 20:35.030
Take your receipt

20:35.070 --> 20:36.960
and claim it at the nearest branch.

20:36.960 --> 20:37.680
In a month,

20:37.750 --> 20:38.750
the Ye Xing caravan

20:38.750 --> 20:39.790
guarantees on-time delivery

20:39.790 --> 20:41.120
within Ye's territory.

20:41.310 --> 20:42.310
Cash on delivery.

20:43.310 --> 20:44.510
Here is your receipt.

21:16.030 --> 21:17.070
Prayer tree.

21:17.790 --> 21:18.750
Yin-Yang Tree

21:24.110 --> 21:24.790
Xiao Wuyi,

21:25.590 --> 21:28.070
could it be that you're actually not dead?

21:30.440 --> 21:31.700
Listen to my analysis.

21:32.310 --> 21:32.840
Firstly,

21:33.480 --> 21:35.160
I didn't even see your body.

21:36.510 --> 21:37.590
Maybe you felt that

21:38.640 --> 21:40.370
being Xiao Wuyi in this life was

21:40.640 --> 21:41.570
too exhausting,

21:42.110 --> 21:43.570
so you wanted to take a rest

21:44.160 --> 21:45.560
and found a place to hide.

21:46.640 --> 21:48.040
When you are well rested,

21:48.480 --> 21:49.810
you will come back to me.

21:52.640 --> 21:54.040
Doesn't that make sense?

21:56.240 --> 21:56.840
Secondly,

21:58.160 --> 21:59.070
you promised me

21:59.550 --> 22:00.680
you would come back.

22:01.400 --> 22:02.660
You have accomplished

22:05.070 --> 22:06.110
everything else.

22:07.880 --> 22:09.880
Xiao Wuyi is always a man of his word.

22:10.550 --> 22:11.610
You couldn't break

22:11.920 --> 22:13.320
your promise on this one,

22:14.030 --> 22:14.710
right?

22:16.160 --> 22:17.310
Why does she feel

22:18.440 --> 22:20.110
so familiar to me?

22:22.270 --> 22:25.330
Why am I feeling an inexplicable heartache
and crying?

23:07.590 --> 23:09.520
But even if you broke your promise,

23:10.270 --> 23:12.270
when we meet in heaven in the future,

23:13.200 --> 23:14.600
I will still forgive you.

23:15.830 --> 23:19.030
You had such a hard,

23:20.160 --> 23:20.890
tiring life.

23:22.790 --> 23:24.520
So I won't blame you for wanting

23:25.240 --> 23:26.070
to rest early.

23:32.200 --> 23:33.200
What do you think?

23:33.640 --> 23:34.640
Am I so generous?

23:36.350 --> 23:37.310
You were lucky

23:39.110 --> 23:40.370
to have me as your wife.

23:46.510 --> 23:47.240
Xiao Wuyi,

23:50.350 --> 23:51.310
I miss you.

23:54.510 --> 23:56.240
I promised you my eternal love.

23:57.680 --> 23:58.790
If you can hear me,

23:59.550 --> 24:00.810
just turn into the wind

24:00.830 --> 24:01.790
or the rain

24:03.160 --> 24:04.490
and meet me in my dreams.

24:09.960 --> 24:11.360
My wish came true so soon?

24:31.640 --> 24:33.480
The younger generation is getting worse.

24:33.480 --> 24:36.140
Go back and practice more
if you want to catch me.

24:48.830 --> 24:51.050
♪ Weave our devotion
into a melody of two hearts ♪

24:51.070 --> 24:53.370
♪ Mirror a gaze of stars and moon ♪

24:53.710 --> 24:56.980
♪ Forever illuminate each other's nights ♪

24:55.240 --> 24:55.970
Are you okay?

24:56.270 --> 24:57.000
Thank you.

24:58.840 --> 25:01.360
♪ The truest, most profound affection ♪

25:01.390 --> 25:03.390
♪ An eternal vow ♪

25:02.830 --> 25:03.830
If this is all he's got,

25:03.780 --> 25:08.190
♪ To be each other's forever ♪

25:04.160 --> 25:06.220
how dare he want to replace Xiao Wuyi?

25:08.790 --> 25:09.270
Hold on...

25:08.930 --> 25:13.230
♪ You enter my dreams,
permeating the crevices of my heart ♪

25:13.490 --> 25:15.490
♪ Every inch of longing ♪

25:15.520 --> 25:19.230
♪ Tugs at unspeakable fantasies ♪

25:19.260 --> 25:23.360
♪ Know that your heart is my heart ♪

25:23.740 --> 25:25.990
♪ Cherishing each other ♪

25:26.010 --> 25:30.600
♪ We will never be alone ♪

25:32.000 --> 25:33.750
♪ In the endless stream of time ♪

25:33.780 --> 25:36.610
♪ My life's every wish is for you ♪

25:36.640 --> 25:41.600
♪ All the sweet nothings in the world
fall short ♪

25:42.430 --> 25:44.110
♪ As time flows gently ♪

25:44.140 --> 25:46.750
♪ Hold each other and seal our vows ♪

25:46.780 --> 25:48.320
♪ Whatever the path ♪

25:48.340 --> 25:52.600
♪ I just want to be with you
for all time ♪

25:51.000 --> 25:53.350
-Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu,
-Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu,

25:52.890 --> 25:54.480
♪ A lifelong promise ♪

25:54.000 --> 25:55.550
-pledge the eternal love.
-pledge the eternal love.

25:54.500 --> 25:57.170
♪ My life's every moment is for you ♪

25:57.190 --> 25:59.190
♪ After all of it ♪

25:59.220 --> 26:02.030
♪ May all your dreams be realized ♪

26:03.070 --> 26:04.440
♪ Just you and me ♪

26:04.460 --> 26:07.640
♪ From dawn to dusk, year after year ♪

26:08.080 --> 26:13.850
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

26:17.830 --> 26:18.640
Come take a look.

26:18.640 --> 26:19.940
Freshly steamed buns and stuffed buns.

26:19.940 --> 26:20.670
Look.

26:23.040 --> 26:24.510
They're freshly made and hot.

26:24.510 --> 26:25.570
Really delicious.

26:38.070 --> 26:39.130
Nanxing! Nanxing!

26:39.590 --> 26:41.650
I think I just saw the Heir's Consort.

26:43.200 --> 26:44.480
There's no way.

26:44.790 --> 26:45.680
Her Ladyship was in Cangwu County

26:45.680 --> 26:47.160
when she wrote me last time.

26:47.160 --> 26:47.680
But...

26:47.920 --> 26:48.850
As you also know,

26:49.160 --> 26:49.960
both Jiankang

26:50.070 --> 26:51.240
and the Northern Border

26:51.240 --> 26:53.640
are places of heartbreak for Her Ladyship.

26:54.790 --> 26:55.550
Now, Her Ladyship

26:55.550 --> 26:57.280
prefers to stay in warm places.

26:57.510 --> 26:58.370
But just now...

27:00.550 --> 27:01.160
Mr. Jing.

27:02.510 --> 27:04.070
Did you record the accounts wrong again?

27:04.070 --> 27:04.920
No way.

27:05.440 --> 27:07.550
The inventory and the numbers don't match.

27:07.550 --> 27:08.110
Come with me.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.710
I'll go take a look. Let's go.

27:31.880 --> 27:33.770
[Black Iron Sword]

27:46.720 --> 27:47.680
This is

27:48.640 --> 27:49.840
the Black Iron Sword.

27:53.920 --> 27:54.510
My Lady!

27:55.640 --> 27:58.440
This is the Black Iron Sword
I forged for Xiao Wuyi.

27:58.640 --> 28:00.160
Where is the person who wanted this sword?

28:00.160 --> 28:01.140
When did he or she come?

28:01.140 --> 28:02.400
H-He came this morning.

28:02.400 --> 28:03.380
What did he look like?

28:03.380 --> 28:04.680
What kind of clothes was he in?

28:04.680 --> 28:05.440
He wore

28:06.080 --> 28:08.480
an Imperial Guard uniform
and a scary mask.

28:09.680 --> 28:11.550
The one I sent
to supervise Beifu this time

28:11.550 --> 28:13.480
is my most trusted
Imperial Guard Commander.

28:13.480 --> 28:15.350
He used to be a member of Beifu, too.

28:15.350 --> 28:17.110
He was injured on the battlefield,

28:17.110 --> 28:17.970
and I saved him.

28:18.320 --> 28:20.050
Then we became sworn brothers.

28:47.920 --> 28:50.060
[Xuanzheng Hall]

28:54.720 --> 28:56.510
Xiao Wuyi is not dead, right?

28:57.200 --> 28:57.960
Where is he?

28:58.070 --> 28:59.400
What on earth happened?

29:01.270 --> 29:02.070
You may leave.

29:02.350 --> 29:03.080
Understood.

29:11.310 --> 29:12.000
Xiao Wuyi,

29:12.440 --> 29:14.300
let me be your strongest support.

29:14.590 --> 29:15.270
You and I

29:15.830 --> 29:17.160
will walk the same path.

29:27.020 --> 29:27.710
Xiao Wuyi,

29:27.150 --> 29:30.570
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

29:28.240 --> 29:30.070
I don't just want
to walk the same path as you.

29:30.070 --> 29:30.920
I want to be

29:31.230 --> 29:34.900
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

29:31.440 --> 29:32.970
together with you forever.

29:35.010 --> 29:39.380
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

29:39.740 --> 29:42.430
♪ So desolate ♪

29:43.010 --> 29:46.680
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

29:46.700 --> 29:50.240
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

29:50.430 --> 29:55.770
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

29:50.510 --> 29:51.640
Do you admit defeat?

29:56.410 --> 29:59.850
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

29:59.870 --> 30:03.870
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

30:04.000 --> 30:07.720
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

30:04.480 --> 30:04.880
Jiayu!

30:07.740 --> 30:11.440
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

30:08.240 --> 30:09.500
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

30:11.690 --> 30:14.510
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

30:12.530 --> 30:13.260
Grand Tutor.

30:14.540 --> 30:17.030
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

30:17.290 --> 30:21.460
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

30:21.480 --> 30:25.080
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

30:25.330 --> 30:27.100
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

30:27.330 --> 30:29.950
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

30:29.970 --> 30:32.640
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

30:31.310 --> 30:31.960
Xiao Wuyi!

30:32.510 --> 30:33.880
Give Yaoyao back to me.

30:32.900 --> 30:37.140
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

30:33.960 --> 30:34.640
Xiao Wuyi!

30:37.470 --> 30:41.640
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

30:37.550 --> 30:38.240
Xiao Wuyi,

30:39.110 --> 30:40.790
husband and wife share the same fate.

30:40.790 --> 30:42.070
I only want you to live.

30:41.950 --> 30:46.790
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

30:43.200 --> 30:44.400
Having you by my side,

30:45.680 --> 30:47.880
I, Xiao Wuyi, have no regrets in my life.

31:00.430 --> 31:03.850
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

31:03.510 --> 31:04.550
There was wind in the valley

31:04.160 --> 31:07.830
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

31:05.110 --> 31:06.840
from a karst cave underground.

31:07.310 --> 31:08.440
When Xiao Wuyi was badly injured,

31:07.940 --> 31:12.310
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

31:09.200 --> 31:11.000
he happened to fall into the cave.

31:11.000 --> 31:13.160
A dead end turned into a way of survival.

31:12.670 --> 31:15.360
♪ So desolate ♪

31:14.440 --> 31:15.000
However,

31:15.940 --> 31:19.610
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

31:16.640 --> 31:18.440
it was too late when we found him.

31:19.630 --> 31:23.170
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

31:19.680 --> 31:21.080
He was barely breathing.

31:23.360 --> 31:28.700
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

31:32.000 --> 31:34.640
You were physically and mentally exhausted
from searching for him,

31:34.640 --> 31:36.040
with a persistent fever.

31:36.240 --> 31:37.920
You were so sick and barely hanging on.

31:37.920 --> 31:39.580
How could I possibly tell you?

31:42.400 --> 31:43.920
Also, that miraculous doctor's
treatment method

31:43.920 --> 31:45.580
was too eerie and terrifying.

31:46.830 --> 31:48.830
Neither Xiao Yao nor I had much hope.

31:49.480 --> 31:50.830
Instead of letting you know

31:50.830 --> 31:53.200
that he died
from having his chest and skull opened,

31:53.200 --> 31:53.730
I thought

31:54.510 --> 31:56.170
he would prefer you to believe

31:56.480 --> 31:57.920
that he died a hero.

32:03.310 --> 32:04.070
No.

32:05.640 --> 32:07.500
I asked him to cling to life for me.

32:08.880 --> 32:11.160
I made him hold his last breath for me.

32:12.680 --> 32:14.740
Even if he couldn't hold on in the end,

32:16.790 --> 32:18.320
I still wouldn't blame him.

32:26.240 --> 32:27.930
When exactly did he wake up?

32:29.480 --> 32:30.480
Three months ago,

32:30.480 --> 32:31.720
he returned to Jiankang,

32:31.720 --> 32:33.720
and I immediately wrote to Xiao Yao.

32:34.480 --> 32:36.200
With Hongzhou's flood season approaching,

32:36.200 --> 32:38.000
he couldn't return
due to canal construction.

32:38.000 --> 32:39.260
Later, he told me that,

32:39.720 --> 32:40.960
since Wuyi survived,

32:41.480 --> 32:42.830
it was fine to meet him later.

32:42.830 --> 32:44.560
He asked me to find you quickly.

32:45.160 --> 32:48.290
But I knew you didn't want to hear
any news from Jiankang.

32:48.480 --> 32:50.720
So I sent a message
through Miraculous Craft.

32:50.720 --> 32:51.480
In the end,

32:52.350 --> 32:53.880
you still didn't come back.

32:54.400 --> 32:56.310
If the little emperor of Northern Qin
hadn't happened to die,

32:56.310 --> 32:58.440
finally giving you a reason to return,

32:58.510 --> 33:00.640
I really would have had to send someone

33:00.750 --> 33:01.750
to get you back.

33:03.660 --> 33:04.450
The mask...

33:06.070 --> 33:07.270
What's with the mask?

33:08.030 --> 33:10.000
Xiao Wuyi has lost
all his martial arts skills now,

33:10.000 --> 33:12.110
yet he insists on going
to the Northern Border.

33:12.110 --> 33:13.240
A resurrected

33:13.640 --> 33:15.240
Xiao Wuyi without memories—

33:15.310 --> 33:18.040
how would the Northern Qin's spies
deal with him?

33:18.550 --> 33:20.680
Many people in the army know Xiao Wuyi.

33:21.110 --> 33:23.070
I don't want to see
any accidents happen before he

33:23.070 --> 33:24.400
remembers everything.

33:26.550 --> 33:27.200
Yaoyao,

33:28.270 --> 33:29.350
you are his consort

33:30.270 --> 33:31.200
and his wife.

33:32.240 --> 33:33.550
The road ahead is

33:35.030 --> 33:35.960
yours to decide.

33:37.480 --> 33:38.110
Mao.

33:40.200 --> 33:41.000
Thank you.

34:07.030 --> 34:07.890
It's Xiao Wuyi.

34:51.630 --> 34:53.360
May Lejun be healthy and happy.

34:54.000 --> 34:56.000
May Mao and I have our wishes

34:56.480 --> 34:58.000
come true year after year.

35:06.590 --> 35:07.590
Thank you, sir!

35:26.450 --> 35:31.080
♪ Hear the heartbeat by my side ♪

35:32.280 --> 35:37.430
♪ Like your rush of passion toward me ♪

35:37.990 --> 35:43.080
♪ A toast to our romantic encounter ♪

35:40.320 --> 35:41.920
The Beifu Army shall forge ahead bravely

35:41.920 --> 35:43.050
and be unstoppable!

35:43.110 --> 35:45.110
♪ I am here only for you ♪

35:45.130 --> 35:48.390
♪ Even though I know
tremendous danger lies ahead ♪

35:48.550 --> 35:53.000
♪ If you could fill the empty spaces
in my memories ♪

35:54.280 --> 35:54.880
Yaoyao,

35:54.350 --> 35:56.810
♪ Only you would stay with me ♪

35:55.840 --> 35:57.320
no matter who tries
to take you away in the future,

35:56.830 --> 35:59.730
♪ My heartbeat will never fade ♪

35:58.110 --> 35:59.710
I will never let you go again.

35:59.880 --> 36:02.680
♪ If I could ask for one blessing ♪

36:02.760 --> 36:05.160
♪ With all the longing I hold ♪

36:05.390 --> 36:08.200
♪ It leads me back to you again ♪

36:08.220 --> 36:11.230
♪ With you as my way,
no distance is too far ♪

36:11.260 --> 36:14.150
♪ The wishes left unsaid ♪

36:14.170 --> 36:16.900
♪ A love I can't let go ♪

36:15.070 --> 36:17.270
Whether you achieve great success
in the future

36:17.270 --> 36:19.900
♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

36:17.400 --> 36:18.930
or are cursed by the masses,

36:19.550 --> 36:20.630
I will always be by your side.

36:19.950 --> 36:23.190
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

36:21.800 --> 36:23.400
I, Xie Jiayu, always keep my word.

36:23.390 --> 36:26.970
♪ To make it come true ♪

36:45.550 --> 36:48.350
♪ If I could ask for one blessing ♪

36:48.430 --> 36:50.840
♪ With all the longing I hold ♪

36:51.060 --> 36:53.870
♪ It leads me back to you again ♪

36:53.890 --> 36:56.900
♪ With you as my way,
no distance is too far ♪

36:56.930 --> 36:59.820
♪ The wishes left unsaid ♪

36:59.850 --> 37:02.570
♪ A love I can't let go ♪

37:02.620 --> 37:05.260
♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

37:05.340 --> 37:08.580
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

37:08.610 --> 37:12.190
♪ To make it come true ♪

37:20.760 --> 37:21.630
Xiao Wuyi!

37:23.600 --> 37:27.980
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

37:28.010 --> 37:31.260
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

37:31.310 --> 37:34.100
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

37:34.120 --> 37:37.120
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

37:37.150 --> 37:41.200
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

37:42.030 --> 37:44.730
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

37:44.760 --> 37:47.680
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

37:47.700 --> 37:53.230
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

38:11.400 --> 38:12.600
I came back a bit late.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.520
You won't blame me, will you?

38:19.920 --> 38:20.710
No, I won't.

38:23.630 --> 38:25.590
It was so hard to snatch a life back

38:27.510 --> 38:28.630
from hell.

38:55.840 --> 38:57.900
When I got this under the prayer tree,

39:00.760 --> 39:02.560
I only had one thought in my mind.

39:06.110 --> 39:07.970
"I must go to the Northern Border.

39:09.000 --> 39:10.800
Someone is waiting for me there.

39:12.320 --> 39:13.920
I must not break my promise."

39:21.110 --> 39:21.800
Xie Jiayu,

39:23.060 --> 39:26.120
You've promised me eternal love
under the prayer tree.

39:29.400 --> 39:31.060
You can't go back on your word.

39:33.510 --> 39:34.770
I will never betray you

39:35.880 --> 39:37.080
and will never regret it.

39:37.080 --> 39:41.130
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

39:41.150 --> 39:44.640
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

39:44.660 --> 39:47.580
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

39:47.610 --> 39:53.140
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

40:04.000 --> 40:05.150
You pinched me.

40:05.360 --> 40:07.280
Are you trying to hurt your husband?

40:07.280 --> 40:09.320
Rest assured, it's not a dream.

42:42.880 --> 42:43.790
You mean

42:43.920 --> 42:45.840
the child the wet nurse
brought into Prince Qi's Mansion

42:45.840 --> 42:46.840
was dead long ago?

42:46.920 --> 42:49.380
Who was the one
they later replaced him with?

42:49.440 --> 42:50.640
The wet nurse is dead.

42:50.920 --> 42:52.150
Her husband said

42:53.030 --> 42:54.560
they didn't swap him at all.

42:54.760 --> 42:56.090
The child was born weak.

42:57.360 --> 42:58.760
He passed away in a month,

42:58.780 --> 42:59.970
even before they

43:00.030 --> 43:00.920
could swap him.

43:02.510 --> 43:04.800
The wet nurse worried
that if Grand Tutor Xie found out

43:04.800 --> 43:05.800
and punished her,

43:06.030 --> 43:07.890
her whole family would be killed.

43:08.510 --> 43:11.190
So she lied to the Grand Tutor
that the child had been swapped,

43:11.190 --> 43:13.590
but it was actually
still the original one.

43:13.880 --> 43:15.080
The Grand Tutor's son

43:15.610 --> 43:16.920
was gone long ago.

43:24.760 --> 43:25.490
What's more,

43:25.940 --> 43:28.760
I found that Prince Qi and his wife
really loved each other.

43:28.760 --> 43:29.710
The other children were

43:29.710 --> 43:31.510
all born to Prince Qi's Consort.

43:31.510 --> 43:33.070
Only the youngest son was

43:33.410 --> 43:34.570
born to a concubine.

43:35.510 --> 43:36.280
However,

43:36.690 --> 43:39.550
he was raised under the name
of Prince Qi's Consort.

